<!-- Help and Navigation -->
<category>
    <pattern>HELP</pattern>
    <template>
        Here's how to use the CS Career Advisor chatbot:
        
        **Getting Started:**
        • Type "START ASSESSMENT" to begin career guidance
        • Type "LEARN ABOUT JOBS" to get information about specific careers
        
        **Available Commands:**
        • "SOFTWARE DEVELOPER" - Learn about software development careers
        • "DATA SCIENTIST" - Information about data science roles
        • "CYBERSECURITY" - Explore cybersecurity careers
        • "WEB DEVELOPER" - Web development opportunities
        • "SYSTEMS ADMIN" - Systems administration and DevOps
        
        **During Assessment:**
        • Answer questions with the letter or number provided
        • Be honest about your interests and skill level
        • You can restart anytime by typing "START ASSESSMENT"
        
        **Need More Help?**
        • Type "EXAMPLES" to see sample conversations
        • Type "ABOUT" to learn about this chatbot
        
        Ready to explore your career options? Type "START ASSESSMENT" to begin!
    </template>
</category>

<category>
    <pattern>LEARN ABOUT JOBS</pattern>
    <template>
        Here are the computing careers I can help you explore:
        
        **1. SOFTWARE DEVELOPER** - Create applications and solve coding problems
        **2. DATA SCIENTIST** - Analyze data and build predictive models
        **3. CYBERSECURITY SPECIALIST** - Protect systems from security threats
        **4. WEB DEVELOPER** - Build websites and web applications
        **5. SYSTEMS ADMINISTRATOR/DEVOPS** - Manage IT infrastructure and automation
        
        Type the name of any career (e.g., "SOFTWARE DEVELOPER") to learn more, or type "START ASSESSMENT" for personalized recommendations based on your interests!
    </template>
</category>

<!-- About and Examples -->
<category>
    <pattern>ABOUT</pattern>
    <template>
        **CS Career Advisor Chatbot**
        
        I'm designed to help computer science students discover suitable career paths based on their interests, strengths, and preferences.
        
        **My Capabilities:**
        • Assess your interests through guided questions
        • Recommend 5 major computing career paths
        • Provide detailed job information including responsibilities, skills, and salary ranges
        • Offer next steps and career development advice
        
        **Career Areas I Cover:**
        1. Software Development/Engineering
        2. Data Science and Analytics
        3. Cybersecurity
        4. Web Development (Frontend, Backend, Full-stack)
        5. Systems Administration and DevOps
        
        **How I Work:**
        I use your responses to assessment questions to match you with the most suitable career paths, then provide comprehensive information to help you make informed decisions about your future.
        
        Ready to start? Type "START ASSESSMENT" or "HELP" for more options!
    </template>
</category>

<category>
    <pattern>EXAMPLES</pattern>
    <template>
        **Sample Conversation Examples:**
        
        **Example 1 - Software Development Path:**
        User: "START ASSESSMENT"
        Bot: [Asks interest questions]
        User: "A" (Creating applications and solving coding problems)
        Bot: [Asks about programming experience]
        User: "2" (Intermediate level)
        Bot: [Provides Software Developer career recommendation]
        
        **Example 2 - Data Science Path:**
        User: "START ASSESSMENT"
        Bot: [Asks interest questions]
        User: "B" (Analyzing data and finding patterns)
        Bot: [Asks about math comfort]
        User: "1" (Love mathematics)
        Bot: [Provides Data Scientist career recommendation]
        
        **Example 3 - Direct Career Inquiry:**
        User: "WEB DEVELOPER"
        Bot: [Asks about frontend vs backend preference]
        User: "1" (Frontend)
        Bot: [Provides Frontend Web Developer information]
        
        **Quick Commands:**
        • "SOFTWARE DEVELOPER" - Direct career info
        • "CYBERSECURITY" - Security career details
        • "HELP" - Usage instructions
        
        Try starting your own assessment now with "START ASSESSMENT"!
    </template>
</category>

